name: TEST
description: TEST

name: Tuberfiend
description: Tuberfiend is a mischievous potato creature crowned with a tiny golden crown, featuring dragon-like horns, claws, and wings that hint at its playful yet powerful nature.

name: Mermash
description: Mermash is a joyful potato mermaid, her hair adorned with vibrant flowers, a shimmering pink tail, and a radiant smile that brings a touch of underwater magic to any scene.

name: Spudshade
description: SpudShade is a mysterious and stoic potato warrior, adorned with a horned helmet and dark cloak, wielding a sword with quiet determination.

name: Starchrot
description: Starchrot is a cheerful yet spooky potato character stitched together with scars, brandishing a pitchfork, and sporting a skull and bone on his head, embodying the playful spirit of a friendly undead.

name: Russet_Sage
description: Russet Sage is a wise and cheerful potato wizard, dressed in a flowing purple robe and hat, wielding a magical staff and holding a small potato, ready to share his arcane knowledge with a smile.

name: Tearytater
description: Tearytater is a small, sad-eyed potato with a perpetually frowning face, dressed in a drooping, tattered wizard's hat, and holding a weathered trident. His teary sky-blue eyes are a constant reminder of the deep sorrow he carries from the Sadness Sea.

name: Teardrop
description: Teardrop is a melancholic potato with shimmering blue eyes, constantly shedding tears that glisten like stars, embodying a deep and profound sadness.

name: Mashie
description: Mashie is a joyful and resilient potato with sparkling blue eyes, always giving a double thumbs-up, ready to lift spirits with his infectious positivity.

name: Gaspytater
description: Gaspytater is a wide-eyed, startled potato adventurer, always on the edge of surprise, with his trusty gear and a quirky flying companion by his side.

name: Winkypuff
description: Winkypuff is a playful and charming potato with a cheeky wink and a sprout of leaves, always ready to brighten everyone's day with a burst of enthusiasm.

name: Giggletuber
description: Giggletuber is a hilariously joyful potato, always laughing so hard that tears stream down his face, spreading infectious laughter wherever he goes.

name: Tater Terror
description: Tater Terror is a menacing and monstrous potato overlord with glowing purple eyes, razor-sharp fangs, and a terrifying presence that commands fear and destruction on the battlefield.

name: Zombie Tater
description: Zombie Tater is an adorably eerie potato with a stitched-up body, lifeless eyes, and a sprout growing from its head, embodying a quirky mix of cuteness and creepiness.

name: Spudvil
description: Spudvil is an adorably devilish potato with tiny wings, a trident, and a mischievous smile that hints at his playful and slightly wicked nature.

name: Spud Zombino
description: Spud Zombino is a frantic and eerie potato zombie with glowing eyes, decayed limbs, and a haunting expression that sends shivers down anyone's spine.

name: Zombispud
description: Zombispud is a quirky and undead potato with stitched-up scars, glowing eyes, and a tattered hat, wandering around with a comically spooky expression.

name: Tendrilato
description: Tendrilato is an otherworldly potato with massive, hypnotic eyes and eerie tendrils sprouting from his body, wielding a twisted staff that pulses with dark energy.

name: Tuberthulu Jr.
description: Tuberthulu Jr. is a hauntingly cute potato with enormous, glowing red eyes and squirming tentacles, blending an unsettling charm with eldritch mystery.

name: Chompy
description: Chompy is a sturdy and cheerful potato warrior with tiny fangs, a rustic hat, and a pitchfork, always ready to defend his friends with a big smile on his face.

name: Dractato
description: Dractato is a whimsical potato dressed in a dragon costume with tiny wings and horns, ready to unleash his playful imagination and charm on any adventure.

name: Firewing
description: Firewing is a lively potato adorned in a vibrant dragon costume, complete with fiery wings and horns, exuding a playful yet fierce spirit.

name: Orcy
description: Orcy is a playful and mischievous potato with pointed ears, tiny fangs, and a cheeky grin, embodying the spirit of a fun-loving orc.

name: Spudbulk
description: Spudbulk is a massive, muscular potato warrior adorned with vines and vegetable armor, exuding raw power and a fierce determination to protect his homeland.

name: Spudwhisperer
description: Spudwhisperer is a heroic potato with vibrant green hair and a flowing cape, exuding an aura of calm strength and a deep connection to the earth.

name: GizmoTuber
description: GizmoTuber is a technologically advanced potato with a wizard's hat, covered in futuristic gadgets and wires, blending magic and machinery in a quirky, inventive way.

name: Crispyglow
description: Crispyglow is a radiant potato princess adorned with a royal crown and a vibrant flower, exuding a warm and gentle light that brightens her surroundings.

name: Spudstorm
description: Spudstorm is a dynamic potato with spiky sprouts and swirling icy energy, always ready to unleash a whirlwind of frosty power on the battlefield.

name: Potatomun
description: Potatomun is an adorable potato dragon hybrid with vibrant blue-green scales, tiny wings, and a heart-shaped marking, radiating a mix of cuteness and magical charm.

name: Mashwhirlwind
description: Mashwhirlwind is an energetic potato with spiky sprouts and a leafy crown, surrounded by a swirling aura of vibrant energy, ready to spin into action with unstoppable force.

name: Spudasaur
description: Spudasaur is a formidable potato creature with a gem-encrusted body, sharp fangs, and vibrant foliage, radiating ancient power and a connection to the earth's primal forces.

name: Taterufo
description: Taterufo is an irresistibly cute potato with alien-like antennae and sparkling eyes, radiating a cosmic charm that's out of this world.

name: Webspud
description: Webspud is an adorable potato with bright eyes and green, spider-like legs, always ready to crawl into action with a cheerful smile.

name: Little Spudnaut
description: Little Spudnaut is an adorable potato astronaut with a gleaming helmet and wide, curious eyes, ready to explore the wonders of the universe.

name: Alienator
description: Alienator is a charming potato with extraterrestrial sprouts and starry eyes, combining earthly cuteness with a touch of cosmic wonder.

name: Captain Spud
description: Captain Spud is a brave and adventurous potato astronaut equipped with high-tech gear and a determined smile, ready to lead his crew through the vastness of space.

name: Spudric the Royal
description: Spudric the Royal is a majestic and imposing potato king, adorned in lavish armor and jewels, wielding a scepter that symbolizes his unchallenged authority and royal power.

name: The Spellblade
description: The Spellblade is a dashing potato mage-warrior, wielding a glowing enchanted sword and wearing a wizard's hat, ready to cast spells and strike down foes with a blend of magic and might.

name: Taterleaf
description: Taterleaf is a mystical potato druid adorned with leafy patterns and a magical hat, channeling the forces of nature to protect and heal.

name: Mashking
description: Mashking is a regal potato with a crown of mashed potatoes, wielding a golden trident, and exuding wisdom and authority as the ruler of all potato-kind.

name: Fryboo
description: Fryboo is a noble and determined potato knight shaped like a box of fries, wielding a magical staff and ready to protect his fellow spuds with unwavering bravery.

name: Frymagic
description: Frymagic is a cheerful and enchanting potato with a box of golden fries and a magical wand, spreading joy and a sprinkle of magic wherever they go.

name: Fryshock
description: Fryshock is a mysterious potato wizard clad in a dark robe, wielding a trident staff, and ready to cast surprising and powerful spells.

name: Spudwest
description: Spudwest is a sharp-shooting potato cowboy, armed with twin revolvers, a steampunk monocle, and a trusty star-shaped companion, ready to bring justice to the Wild Spud West.

name: Huntato
description: Huntato is a keen-eyed potato sniper, equipped with a scoped rifle, camouflaged in wilderness gear, ready to strike with precision from any distance in the spud-filled forests.

name: Desperado
description: Desperado is a tough and determined potato gunslinger, clad in a cowboy hat and a star badge, with revolvers ready to uphold justice in the wild west of Spudville.

name: Spudrik the Brave
description: Spudrik the Brave is a courageous potato warrior, equipped with a Viking helmet, axe, and shield, ready to conquer any battle with a smile on his face.

name: Mashwhip
description: Mashwhip is a cheerful potato warrior, topped with a swirl of whipped mash and wielding a glowing sword, ready to spread joy and defend his friends.

name: Starchwood the Mighty
description: Starchwood the Mighty is a steadfast potato warrior adorned with ornate armor, a commanding mustache, and a glowing blade, exuding a powerful and heroic presence.

name: Sensei Spudster
description: Sensei Spudster is a disciplined and determined potato ninja, armed with a sharp katana and donned in traditional warrior garb, ready to defend with honor and precision.

name: Ninja Nugget
description: Ninja Nugget is a stealthy and agile potato warrior, masked and ready to strike with his gleaming blade, embodying the art of silent precision.

name: Sir Happy Sword
description: Sir Happy Sword is the ultimate legendary hero, radiating pure joy and unwavering courage, clad in gleaming armor with a star-emblazoned shield and a sword held high, ready to lead with a smile and protect his fellow spuds.

name: Sir Peelgood the Protector
description: Sir Peelgood the Protector stands vigilant in his sturdy armor, with a resolute expression and a sword ready to defend his spud comrades from any threat that dares approach.

name: Professor Dimpledwarf
description: Professor Dimpledwarf is a wise and gentle potato sage, carrying a sack of knowledge and a staff, ready to guide others with his twinkling eyes and cheerful demeanor.

name: Spudblossom
description: Spudblossom is a joyful and heavenly potato adorned with a glowing halo and delicate wings, radiating warmth and happiness like a blooming flower.

name: Halotater
description: Halotater is a serene and angelic potato with a golden halo and soft wings, spreading peace and kindness wherever it goes.

name: Yam the Healer
description: Yam the Healer is a charming and magical potato mage, adorned in a pointed wizard hat and wielding a staff with a star, ready to cast powerful healing spells with a warm and joyful smile.

name: Sneakroot
description: Sneakroot, the mysterious potato thief, shrouded in a purple cloak, wields a sword and shield, always poised for a cunning and daring heist.

name: Solana
description: Solana, the guardian potato, casts radiant shields with a glance from her glowing blue eyes, her sapphire crown pulsing with ancient magic as she protects her team from harm.

name: Solarchip
description: Solarchip's helmet reflects deep space's vibrant colors, while his shimmering flippers and tail radiate cosmic energy, surrounded by sparkling stars and shapes that enhance his intergalactic charm.

name: Taterlance
description: Taterlance, the fearless potato guardian, races across the land on his swift steed, Spudhoof, wielding lightning magic to protect all!

name: Totator
description: Totator, the mystical techno-potato, harnesses ancient magic and futuristic machinery, his glowing eye revealing secrets of time!

name: Hallowtina
description: Hallowtina, the adorable potato, is all set for Halloween in her festive pilgrim hat adorned with autumn decorations. With sparkling eyes, rosy cheeks, and a pumpkin basket in hand, she proudly waves her ghost flag, ready for some spooky trick-or-treating fun! Hallowtina can summon glowing star spirits that boost allies' morale and frighten enemies with charm.

name: Hallowtato
description: Hallowtato, the cheerful potato, dons a witch's hat and cloak, holding a pumpkin basket and a spooky skull flag. Surrounded by bats, his glowing eyes and joyful expression show he's ready for Halloween fun and trick-or-treating! Hallowtato conjures explosive pumpkin bombs that detonate upon impact, scattering fiery projectiles.

name: Howlroot
description: Howlroot is a fierce, potato-shaped werewolf with sharp fangs, intense brows, and a pumpkin-topped hat. Wielding a pitchfork, his skill is howling to boost his strength, increasing his attack power with every full moon.

name: Endzone Eater
description: Endzone Eater, the zombie potato football player, lumbers down the field in his torn jersey and helmet. With glowing eyes and stitched limbs, his special skill is "Skull Smash," delivering bone-crushing tackles that leave opponents in pieces!

name: Websprout
description: Websprout is a mischievous potato hero dressed as a spider for Halloween, wearing a dark web-themed cloak and a skull emblem. He uses his Web Sling skill to trap enemies in sticky webs.

name: Wrapped Worryroot
description: Wrapped Worryroot is a nervous little potato wrapped tightly in mummy bandages. With wide, anxious eyes, she's always on edge, worrying about unraveling. Wrapped Worryroots skill, "Frightened Wrap," allows her to tighten her bandages in panic, creating a quick defensive shield that can block incoming attacks for a short time.

name: Pumpkinette
description: Pumpkinette, a joyful fusion of potato and pumpkin, spreads festive magic wherever she goes. Her leafy cape sways as tiny spirits dance around her. Skill: "Harvest Glow"  She radiates a warm light that boosts allies' energy and morale. Pumpkinette throws a Branch Shuriken, unleashing playful spirits that enhance her festive magic attack!

name: Soulharvest
description: Soulharvest is a chilling figure, cloaked in darkness with a scythe that gleams under the moonlight. His presence drains the light from any Halloween night. Skill: "Harvest Strike"  With a swing of his scythe, he siphons the life essence of nearby foes.

name: Mia Spudora
description:
[color=#c86fd9] - Rarity: Unique

[color=#b4b4b4]Mia Spudora, the enchanting potato witch, dazzles in her starry purple gown and ornate hat. With glowing eyes, a flowing cape, and magical stars, she's ready to cast spells and charm her way through a spooky Halloween night!

Skills:

Galaxy Storm: Unleashes a storm, raining down explosive stars to obliterate enemies in radiant bursts.

name: Captain Skullcrust
description:
[color=#d7a550] - Rarity: Legendary

[color=#b4b4b4]Captain Skullcrust is a fearsome potato pirate with a skull-emblazoned hat and tattered cloak. His eerie grin strikes terror across the seas. His skill, 

Skills:

Ghostly Barrage: He summons spectral cannonballs to bombard enemies from afar.

name: Whisperhoof
description:
[color=#c86fd9] - Rarity: Unique

[color=#b4b4b4]Whisperhoof, a silent and swift potato horse, drifts through shadows in their tattered cloak. Despite the mummy-like wrappings over their mouth, their presence is hauntingly subtle. 

Skills:

Phantom Gallop: Can sprint at lightning speed, leaving no trace or sound, unseen until it's too late.
